body.description: Get the superior clean you’ve been waiting for with Cottonelle Ultra Clean Toilet Paper, designed to clean three ways in one. The soft, yet strong cleaning ripples are safe for sensitive skin and removes residue that can cause irritation and odor-causing bacteria. The Cadillac of 1-ply toilet paper, Cottonelle Ultra Clean toilet tissue is 3x stronger than the leading value brand in order protect your hands as you cleanup, and is still septic-safe and clog-free. Each Cottonelle Mega Roll has 312 sheets per roll so you can worry less about running out when you or guests at your home need it most. Looking for more ways to feel clean down there after taking care of business? Use Cottonelle flushable wet wipes to feel shower fresh 3x longer***. Conveniently remain stocked on toilet paper by ordering Cottonelle for delivery to your door or pickup curbside. Cottonelle cares about you and our planet. We are proud to be FSC certified ensuring the forests we source from are responsibly managed to prevent deforestation and help protect the trees and animals that depend on them. We also use fibers that are 100% plant-based and no dyes.*vs. leading value brand regular rolls **vs. leading value brand ***using dry + wet vs dry alone

Why Cottonelle? No matter how you roll, Cottonelle’s sustainable, premium toilet paper and flushable wipes help you feel ahhh-mazing—our soft and strong bathroom essentials meet strict standards to protect forests and the animals and people that depend on them. What’s the difference between Cottonelle Ultra Clean Toilet Paper and Cottonelle Ultra Comfort Toilet Paper? Our Ultra Clean toilet tissue is designed to remove more residue* to help you feel confidently clean. Our Ultra Comfort toilet tissue is designed to absorb more moisture* to help you feel comfortably clean. *vs. leading value brand What’s CleaningRipples Texture? Those little ripples are designed to help you clean the best so you can feel your best! They hold shape when wet, which means removing more residue* (Ultra Clean) and absorbing more moisture* (Ultra Comfort) with every wipe. *vs. leading value brand What’s a Mega Roll? It’s mega-amazing: Each Mega Roll lasts 4x longer than the leading brand’s regular roll, so you don’t have to change rolls as often. How many square feet are in Cottonelle Toilet Paper? Cottonelle is designed with you in mind, and that means tons of different sizes to help you find the perfect roll. Giant + Roll: 30.60 square feet per roll. Mega Roll: 32.90 square feet per roll. Family Mega Roll: 40.90 square feet per roll.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best toilet paper ever made. Honestly.
reviews.reviewText: This is by far the best toilet paper. Hands down. Perfect wipes every time with the soft but strong ripples. This is the only toilet paper I buy now. Any time I'm forced to use that useless one-ply or 2- ply (if I'm lucky) at gas stations, restaurants or hospitals, all I can think about is how much better of a wipe I could get if I had this toilet paper... Truly a shame that large corporations refuse to give us the luxury of a clean bum without wiping till you're bleeding from how rough the 1 and 2 ply toilet paper they have is.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars TMI but the cleaning is what sets ultra clean apart
reviews.reviewText: Cottonelle ultra clean does just that… it wipes you clean. It’s not as soft as some of the extra soft toilet tissue but it’s not rough either. We all know there are times when we need that perfect sweet spot between a good clean wipe and comfort and I believe cottonelle ultra clean found it. We’ve tried all kinds of toilet tissue and this seems to work well for us. It’s durable (as far a toilet tissue goes), wipes up the poop, and doesn’t leave you feeling “raw”. Sorry for the graphic words but we are talking about a good toilet tissue for body waste. :)
